<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>The Anti-Cringe Engineer</title>
    <style>
        body {
            background-color: #000;
            color: #fff;
            font-family: 'Courier New', Courier, monospace; /* طابع تقني أكثر */
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            min-height: 100vh;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 20px;
            text-align: center;
        }
        .container {
            max-width: 600px;
        }
        img.profile {
            width: 150px;
            height: 150px;
            border-radius: 50%;
            border: 1px solid #333;
            margin-bottom: 25px;
            object-fit: cover;
            filter: grayscale(100%); /* لجعلها أكثر غموضاً وجدية */
        }
        h1 {
            font-size: 1.6rem;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
            letter-spacing: 2px;
            text-transform: uppercase;
        }
        p {
            font-size: 0.9rem;
            color: #aaa;
            line-height: 1.8;
            margin-bottom: 35px;
        }
        .tier-buttons {
            display: grid;
            gap: 12px;
            width: 100%;
        }
        .btn-tier {
            background-color: #000;
            color: #fff;
            border: 1px solid #444;
            padding: 18px;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 4px;
            font-size: 0.85rem;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            transition: all 0.4s ease;
        }
        .btn-tier:hover {
            background-color: #fff;
            color: #000;
            border-color: #fff;
        }
        .footer {
            margin-top: 60px;
            font-size: 0.7rem;
            color: #333;
            letter-spacing: 1px;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <div class="container">
        <img src="hero.jpg" alt="DevOps Engineer" class="profile">
        
        <h1>The Anti-Cringe Experiment</h1>
        <p>
            I am a DevOps Engineer launching a social test. <br>
            Does the digital world still value mastery, or has it decayed into pure mediocrity? <br>
            Your support is a vote for logic. Choose your level.
        </p>

        <div class="tier-buttons">
            <a href="https://www.patreon.com/c/theanti_cringeengineer/membership" target="_blank" class="btn-tier">
                Level 1: Anti-Cringe Vote ($1)
            </a>
            <a href="https://www.patreon.com/c/theanti_cringeengineer/membership" target="_blank" class="btn-tier">
                Level 2: Logic Supporter ($10)
            </a>
            <a href="https://www.patreon.com/c/theanti_cringeengineer/membership" target="_blank" class="btn-tier">
                Level 3: Guardian of Intellect ($100)
            </a>
            <a href="https://www.patreon.com/c/theanti_cringeengineer/membership" target="_blank" class="btn-tier">
                Level 4: The Elite Mind ($1000)
            </a>
        </div>

        <div class="footer">
            SYSTEM STATUS: ONLINE | ADANA-NODE | 2026
        </div>
    </div>

</body>
</html>
